commands.name: az automation source-control sync-job stream list
commands.summary: List a list of sync job streams identified by sync job id.
commands.syntax:
az automation source-control sync-job stream list --account
                                                  --resource-group
                                                  --source-control-name
                                                  --sync-job-id
                                                  [--filter]
                                                  [--max-items]
                                                  [--next-token]
examples: az automation source-control sync-job stream list -g rg --automation-account-name myAutomationAccount --source-control-name sourceControl --sync-job-id abcdef01-2345-6789-9bed-a01234567890

commands.name: az automation source-control sync-job stream show
commands.summary: Get a sync job stream identified by stream id.
commands.syntax:
az automation source-control sync-job stream show [--account]
                                                  [--ids]
                                                  [--resource-group]
                                                  [--source-control-name]
                                                  [--stream-id]
                                                  [--subscription]
                                                  [--sync-job-id]
examples: az automation source-control sync-job stream show -g rg --automation-account-name myAutomationAccount --source-control-name sourceControl --sync-job-id abcdef01-2345-6789-9bed-a01234567890 --stream-id b86c5c31-e9fd-4734-8764-ddd6c101e706_00636596855139029522_00000000000000000007
